August 6, 2022 started a journey into the world of waffles @djwafflesmix finally. The brand has exploded and I have served over 4,000 people. Placed in 3 restaurants and bookings are coming in. This wasn't an easy task at all to get here. I been through a lot in my life. Even having my freedom stripped away from me. But my bounce back with GOD being in my corner led to dope people supporting me and helping with this vision. I've done, showcases, podcast, tours for artist, magazine.. now a whole waffle company!!! Thank you @leigh__plainandsimple for all you've done day in day out in this process!! @isetrends you seen the sitcho and said let's get it!! I can name so many people that played huge roles. I'm thankful to have everyone who even gave insight on ideas. But I'm grateful and humble about all the blessings that has come and those that are coming. We all have an expiration date and I'm here to enjoy it as long as I can.
